Instale o git:
	sudo apt install git
Use o terminal para baixar o IAT na pasta desejada:
	git clone https://github.com/alexmorimitsu/IAT.git

Instale o miniconda:
	Seguir o tutorial em https://www.how2shout.com/linux/install-miniconda-on-ubuntu-22-04-lts-jammy-linux/
Fechar o terminal e abrir um novo
Crie um ambiente conda (testado: Python 3.7):
	conda create -n iat python=3.7
Ative o ambiente conda:
	conda activate iat

Instale o pandas:
	conda install pandas
	conda install pandas-datareader
Instale o pillow:
	conda install pillow
Instale o dash:
	conda install -c conda-forge dash-html-components
	pip install dash==2.2.0
Instale o matplotlib:
	pip install matplotlib
Instale o sklearn:
	pip install -U scikit-learn
Faça downgrade do werkzeug para 2.0.3:
	pip uninstall werkzeug
	pip install werkzeug==2.0.3
Faça downgrade do flask para 2.1.3:
	pip uninstall flask
	pip install flask==2.1.3
Instale o dash-bootstrap:
	conda install -c conda-forge dash-bootstrap-components=1.2.1
